metadata.name: Priorities
metadata.description:
Men have priorities and nothing can replace the state of true gamers when there's a war going on the battlefield.

This is a 1/1 artwork especially made with Autodesk Sketchbook as well as Blender with high quality render and packed with rich multi shading colors popping, leaving your eyes and screen craving for more.

True 4k
Res:  3786x4794
